articles.title: Bangladesh-Ireland washed out, South Africa qualify for ODI World Cup - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Ireland needed to win all three matches in the series to stand a chance of claiming the final automatic qualifying place for the World Cup in place of Proteas. | Cricket
articles.content: The first of three one-day internationals between Bangladesh and Ireland ended in a no result after the match was abandoned because of rain, confirming South Africa's place in this year's Cricket Wor… [+1398 chars]
